      "widgets_values": [
        "# ⭐ Z-Image Enhanced — StarNodes Template\n\n**Pipeline:** ① Load Z-Image Turbo models + optional LoRA ➜ ② Prompt & latent size ➜ ③ Star Sampler ➜ ④ Save image ➜ ⑤ Stop & Go (review) ➜ ⑥ SD Upscale Refiner Advanced ➜ ⑦ Save upscaled\n**Requires:** ComfyUI 0.25+ · StarNodes\n\n## 📥 Model Downloads — Z-Image Enhanced\n\n**Diffusion model** ➜ `models/diffusion_models/`\n• [z_image_turbo_bf16.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/resolve/main/split_files/diffusion_models/z_image_turbo_bf16.safetensors) (BF16)\n• [z_image_turbo_int8_convrot.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/resolve/main/split_files/diffusion_models/z_image_turbo_int8_convrot.safetensors) (INT8)\n• [z_image_turbo_nvfp4.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/resolve/main/split_files/diffusion_models/z_image_turbo_nvfp4.safetensors) (NVFP4)\n• FP8: [PLACEHOLDER] — check HuggingFace for FP8 versions of z-image-turbo\n\n**Text encoder** ➜ `models/text_encoders/`\n• [qwen_3_4b_fp8_mixed.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_3_4b_fp8_mixed.safetensors) (FP8)\n• [qwen_3_4b.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/resolve/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_3_4b.safetensors) (BF16)\n\n**VAE** ➜ `models/vae/`\n• [ae.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/resolve/main/split_files/vae/ae.safetensors)\n• SeedVR2,ema_vae_fp16.safetensors https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/SeedVR2/resolve/main/vae/ema_vae_fp16.safetensors\n\n**SeedVR model** ➜ `models/diffusion_models/` https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/SeedVR2/resolve/main/diffusion_models/seedvr2_7b_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors\n• [003_realSR_BSRGAN_DFO_s64w8_SwinIR-M_x2_PSNR.pth](https://openmodeldb.info/models/003-realSR-BSRGAN-DFO-s64w8-SwinIR-M-x2-PSNR)"
